title: List of minor planets discovered using the WISE spacecraft
text: The following is a list of numbered <a href="minor%20planet">minor planet</a>s discovered, co-discovered and re-discovered by the <a href="Wide-field%20Infrared%20Survey%20Explorer">Wide-field Infrared Survey Explorer</a> (WISE), a NASA infrared spaceborne observatory. As of July 2018, the list contains 4093 entries, accredited by the <a href="Minor%20Planet%20Center">Minor Planet Center</a> as discovered by "WISE". Notable discoveries include , , and .
